      <title>最高法院部分支持特朗普豁免权，推迟审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/supreme-court-partially-backs-trump-on-immunity-delaying-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院裁定唐纳德·特朗普因试图推翻 2020 年大选结果而免于受到部分刑事指控，这几乎确保了审判不会在 11 月大选之前进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/supreme-court-partially-backs-trump-on-immunity-delaying-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 14:34:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱表示，如果通胀进一步降温，他将放缓爬行钉住汇率制度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/milei-says-he-would-slow-crawling-peg-if-inflation-cools-further</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱周日晚间概述了他对阿根廷未来货币政策的愿景，他表示，如果通胀降温至一定水平，比索贬值的速度可能会放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/milei-says-he-would-slow-crawling-peg-if-inflation-cools-further</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 14:15:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院允许刷卡费诉讼，对监管机构造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/supreme-court-allows-swipe-fee-challenge-in-blow-to-regulators</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院在一起借记卡刷卡费案件中裁定，一些法规可以在颁布十年甚至更长时间后受到质疑，这对联邦机构的权威造成了新的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/supreme-court-allows-swipe-fee-challenge-in-blow-to-regulators</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 14:02:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国法院将于 9 月前对总理和反对党案件作出裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/thai-court-to-rule-on-pm-top-opposition-party-cases-by-sept</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国宪法法院预计将在 9 月前对两起备受关注的案件作出判决，一起是要求罢免总理斯雷塔·塔维辛的案件，另一起是要求解散反对党前进党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/thai-court-to-rule-on-pm-top-opposition-party-cases-by-sept</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 12:18:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非经济自由斗士联盟抗议联合政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/south-africa-s-eff-plans-protests-against-coalition-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非左翼经济自由战士表示，计划举行抗议活动，以表达对该国新成立的联合政府的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/south-africa-s-eff-plans-protests-against-coalition-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 11:44:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Instagram 和 Facebook 无广告，遭欧盟警告打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/meta-set-for-eu-warning-over-ad-free-instagram-facebook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 因其在 Instagram 和 Facebook 上采用的无广告服务订阅模式而受到警告，在欧盟根据严格的新规则对大型科技公司的最新打击中，该公司可能面临高额罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/meta-set-for-eu-warning-over-ad-free-instagram-facebook</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 08:33:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙与法国左翼对手竞相阻止勒庞势头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/macron-and-french-left-wing-rivals-race-to-stop-far-right-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的中间派联盟和左翼新人民阵线正在考虑是否将候选人从周日的第二轮立法选举中撤出，以阻止占主导地位的极右翼政党掌权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/macron-and-french-left-wing-rivals-race-to-stop-far-right-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 05:49:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登盟友在周末疯狂竞选中拒绝辞职呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/biden-loyalists-dismiss-calls-to-quit-in-frenetic-weekend-blitz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在辩论中表现惨淡，遭到捐助者、顾问、官员和媒体的强烈反对，他们呼吁拜登退出 2024 年大选。拜登的竞选团队正在对此进行反击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/biden-loyalists-dismiss-calls-to-quit-in-frenetic-weekend-blitz</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 22:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚抗议活动致 24 人死亡 鲁托称“我手上没有鲜血”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/kenyan-president-defends-handling-of-deadly-youth-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托为其部署军队平息过去两周全国范围内抗议活动的决定进行辩护，抗议活动已造成至少 24 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/kenyan-president-defends-handling-of-deadly-youth-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 18:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普是总统还是普通公民：为什么最高法院的豁免裁决是一项考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/supreme-court-immunity-decision-could-save-trump-in-2020-election-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院将于周一就唐纳德·特朗普的说法作出裁决，特朗普称自己不会因试图推翻 2020 年大选结果而受到刑事指控，该案件很有可能被退回下级法院进行进一步的法律争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/supreme-court-immunity-decision-could-save-trump-in-2020-election-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
